===Verb===
{{en-verb|becomes|becoming|became|become}}

# {{context|copulative}} To [[begin]] to [[be]]; to come to be; to [[turn into]]
#: ''She '''became''' a doctor when she was 25.''
#: ''The weather will '''become''' cold after the sun goes down.''
# {{transitive}} To look [[attractive]] on, be [[suitable]] for
#: ''That dress really '''becomes''' you.''

